And I'm serious.

344
00:19:02,460 --> 00:19:03,860
But business is business.

345
00:19:04,220 --> 00:19:05,420
This case is simple.

346
00:19:05,420 --> 00:19:06,860
I'll win it for you tomorrow.

347
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:11,460
Ms. Qin,

348
