00:20:28,180 --> 00:20:28,900
Ms. Song!

369
00:20:29,140 --> 00:20:29,740
Quick.

370
00:20:29,780 --> 00:20:30,300
Ms. Song,

371
00:20:30,460 --> 00:20:31,380
although you won the case,

