00:20:48,660 --> 00:20:49,900
The case is won.

382
00:20:50,380 --> 00:20:51,580
As the plaintiff's attorney,

383
00:20:51,700 --> 00:20:52,820
I'll see this through

384
00:20:52,820 --> 00:20:54,340
