385
00:20:54,860 --> 00:20:55,900
Please rest assured.

386
00:20:56,500 --> 00:20:56,980
Let's go.

387
00:20:57,780 --> 00:20:58,940
Excuse me. Let us through.

388
00:20:59,860 --> 00:21:01,740
Ms. Song. Ms. Song!

389
00:21:18,500 --> 00:21:19,340
We won the case.

390
00:21:20,060 --> 00:21:21,260
How about buying me a drink?

391
00:21:22,300 --> 00:21:23,860
I might even tell you

392
00:21:23,980 --> 00:21:25,180
a little secret about Baijian.

393
00:21:26,060 --> 00:21:26,540
Okay.

394
00:21:45,100 --> 00:21:45,700
Why did you want to see me?

395
00:21:46,940 --> 00:21:48,340
How are things going

396
00:21:48,780 --> 00:21:49,820
with what I asked you to handle?

397
00:21:50,620 --> 00:21:52,220
Your mother has been released
on bail pending trial.

398
00:21:52,660 --> 00:21:53,940
I'm still gathering the money.

399
00:21:56,100 --> 00:21:57,300
Then why hasn't she contacted me?

400
00:21:57,660 --> 00:21:58,180
Are you insane?

401
00:21:59,620 --> 00:22:00,700
Her legal troubles aren't resolved,

402
00:22:01,300 --> 00:22:02,860
and you've caused this huge mess!

403
00:22:03,540 --> 00:22:04,380
How could she possibly contact you?

404
00:22:06,700 --> 00:22:07,340
Wenhan,

405
00:22:08,020 --> 00:22:09,140
you need to lay low.

406
00:22:09,780 --> 00:22:11,220
Contact her again later.

407
00:22:13,180 --> 00:22:13,820
What about the money?

408
00:22:17,140 --> 00:22:17,940
I have a few hundred thousand here.

409
00:22:18,300 --> 00:22:19,100
You can take it all.

410
00:22:19,660 --> 00:22:21,380
A few hundred thousand?

411
00:22:22,820 --> 00:22:24,740
Am I a beggar or what?

412
00:22:33,500 --> 00:22:34,820
I need fifty million!

413
00:22:36,300 --> 00:22:37,300
Get it for me soon.

414
00:22:38,660 --> 00:22:39,340
Remember,

415
00:22:40,740 --> 00:22:41,540
the sooner, the better.

416
00:22:42,140 --> 00:22:43,220
Fifty million?

417
00:22:45,180 --> 00:22:47,060
Where am I supposed
to get that much money?

418
00:22:52,900 --> 00:22:55,140
With the power you wield

419
00:22:55,460 --> 00:22:57,660
under Ye Taiting's nose,

420
00:22:59,220 --> 00:23:00,380
that amount

421
00:23:00,620 --> 00:23:02,740
shouldn't be too hard for you, right?

422
00:23:15,540 --> 00:23:16,780
Hurry up!

423
00:23:31,420 --> 00:23:32,380
You're finally here.

424
00:23:32,900 --> 00:23:33,500
Have a seat.

425
00:23:33,900 --> 00:23:34,660
How are you feeling?

426
00:23:34,900 --> 00:23:35,860
I'm doing alright.

427
00:23:36,220 --> 00:23:36,900
What about Wenhan?

428
00:23:37,620 --> 00:23:38,540
I just met him.

429
00:23:38,940 --> 00:23:40,420
He's hiding in a safe place.

430
00:23:41,540 --> 00:23:42,620
Let him lay low for now.

431
00:23:43,660 --> 00:23:45,580
I'll figure something out later.

432
00:23:46,420 --> 00:23:47,940
He's impulsive.

433
00:23:48,300 --> 00:23:49,580
You must take good care of him.

434
00:23:51,820 --> 00:23:52,980
If Wenhan ends up in prison,

435
00:23:55,260 --> 00:23:56,980
I'll feel like there's no point anymore.

436
00:23:58,060 --> 00:23:59,060
Then our family

437
00:24:00,020 --> 00:24:00,940
would truly be finished.

438
00:24:03,620 --> 00:24:04,780
After all I've been through these years,

439
00:24:06,740 --> 00:24:08,580
leaving my own husband and child

440
00:24:09,940 --> 00:24:11,740
to be someone else's wife,

441
00:24:13,300 --> 00:24:14,580
raising another woman's children...

442
00:24:16,060 --> 00:24:18,220
If it all comes to nothing in the end,

443
00:24:18,820 --> 00:24:20,500
I just can't accept it.

444
00:24:24,020 --> 00:24:24,900
Wenzhi.

445
00:24:25,980 --> 00:24:27,020
Don't worry.

446
00:24:28,180 --> 00:24:29,300
We need to plan carefully.

447
00:24:29,860 --> 00:24:31,020
We can start over.

448
00:24:32,060 --> 00:24:33,140
You don't understand.

449
00:24:34,300 --> 00:24:36,380
Now that Song Zhizhi has won her case,

450
00:24:37,540 --> 00:24:38,740
I'm really worried the Song family

