00:24:39,460 --> 00:24:41,020
will make a comeback soon.

452
00:24:42,020 --> 00:24:43,180
But look at us?

453
00:24:43,820 --> 00:24:45,780
One gone, one in prison.

454
00:24:45,980 --> 00:24:47,500
I'm so full of hatred.

455
00:24:48,060 --> 00:24:49,380
I've made up my mind.

456
00:24:50,340 --> 00:24:51,820
Even if I have to fight this out
to the end,

457
00:24:53,180 --> 00:24:54,940
even if I die,

458
00:24:55,980 --> 00:24:57,900
I'm taking them down with me!

459
00:25:15,900 --> 00:25:16,740
It's rare for you to have time

460
00:25:16,860 --> 00:25:17,900
to join us for camping, Ms. Song.

461
00:25:23,700 --> 00:25:24,900
Well, we won the case.

462
00:25:25,140 --> 00:25:25,860
Time for a change of scenery.

463
00:25:26,060 --> 00:25:27,500
Getting out is nice.

464
00:25:28,140 --> 00:25:29,780
You'll love the spot I picked.

465
00:25:30,500 --> 00:25:32,180
I spent a long time

466
00:25:32,260 --> 00:25:33,420
choosing this campsite.

467
00:25:34,100 --> 00:25:35,420
Ji, do you remember?

468
00:25:35,740 --> 00:25:38,220
What was the name of that park

469
00:25:38,220 --> 00:25:39,580
