470
00:25:40,860 --> 00:25:41,900
Winter...

471
00:25:42,180 --> 00:25:42,980
Did we go there often?

472
00:25:46,300 --> 00:25:46,820
Alright then.

473
00:25:47,740 --> 00:25:49,100
We'll wait and see.

474
00:26:01,140 --> 00:26:02,100
Drive slower.

475
00:26:03,340 --> 00:26:03,820
Okay.

476
00:26:34,900 --> 00:26:36,900
You handle this car pretty well.

477
00:27:02,220 --> 00:27:02,700
Have a drink?

478
00:27:03,980 --> 00:27:05,260
I'll have water, thanks.

479
00:27:05,660 --> 00:27:06,100
Be careful.

480
00:27:10,980 --> 00:27:11,660
I'll get it.

481
00:27:13,220 --> 00:27:13,780
Let me.

