00:27:16,780 --> 00:27:18,060
Then I'll go get that bag.

483
00:27:20,660 --> 00:27:21,140
Is it heavy?

484
00:27:21,340 --> 00:27:21,940
Not really.

485
00:27:30,340 --> 00:27:30,820
Let me.

486
00:27:31,900 --> 00:27:32,700
You rest.

487
00:27:38,820 --> 00:27:40,780
I think this spot is nice.

488
00:27:41,140 --> 00:27:42,700
Worth the drive.

489
00:27:46,940 --> 00:27:49,100
It's alright. Nothing too special.

490
00:27:49,180 --> 00:27:50,500
I'll take this over first.

491
00:27:58,340 --> 00:28:00,100
Ji, come have a drink!

492
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:00,820
Let's celebrate.

493
00:28:01,260 --> 00:28:02,980
Sure. Let's have a toast.

494
00:28:04,780 --> 00:28:05,300
Alright.

495
00:28:06,020 --> 00:28:06,620
Okay.

496
00:28:08,500 --> 00:28:08,820
Cheers.

497
00:28:08,940 --> 00:28:09,580
-Cheers.
-Cheers.

498
00:28:09,820 --> 00:28:11,260
To our victory!

499
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:16,380
Ziming,

500
00:28:16,780 --> 00:28:18,180
