502
00:28:19,980 --> 00:28:20,300
No, thanks.

503
00:28:20,700 --> 00:28:21,420
It's fine.

504
00:28:23,860 --> 00:28:25,020
It's just that we drove all this way,

505
00:28:25,180 --> 00:28:26,020
searched around,

506
00:28:26,660 --> 00:28:28,100
and this place doesn't seem
that special.

507
00:28:28,420 --> 00:28:29,820
Who says it's not special?

508
00:28:30,580 --> 00:28:33,220
This is a little secret
between me and Baijian.

509
00:28:36,780 --> 00:28:38,100
We took a photo

510
00:28:38,140 --> 00:28:39,940
under this tree ten years ago.

511
00:28:40,380 --> 00:28:41,740
We promised each other

512
00:28:42,300 --> 00:28:43,620
