under this same tree.

515
00:28:48,180 --> 00:28:49,340
Ji, remember?

516
00:28:50,220 --> 00:28:51,020
I don't remember.

517
00:28:52,100 --> 00:28:53,500
How can you not remember?

518
00:28:53,780 --> 00:28:54,820
I even have the photo here.

519
00:28:55,140 --> 00:28:56,060
Let me find it.

520
00:29:01,500 --> 00:29:02,220
Look.

521
00:29:06,860 --> 00:29:09,100
Ji really wasn't as handsome back then
as he is now.

522
00:29:09,100 --> 00:29:09,740
Look.

