00:29:16,220 --> 00:29:16,780
Zhizhi,

524
00:29:17,460 --> 00:29:18,180
these are done.

525
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:19,140
Have some.

526
00:29:29,660 --> 00:29:30,620
Have something to eat.

527
00:29:32,780 --> 00:29:33,260
Not hungry.

528
00:29:34,260 --> 00:29:35,980
I'm hungry. I'll have it.

529
00:29:40,780 --> 00:29:42,780
I really never thought

530
00:29:43,140 --> 00:29:45,620
we'd get the chance to come back here,

531
00:29:45,900 --> 00:29:48,060
