539
00:30:07,180 --> 00:30:07,620
No, I'm not.

540
00:30:11,340 --> 00:30:12,460
Then I'll take a walk with you.

541
00:30:14,260 --> 00:30:14,660
Let's go.

542
00:30:14,780 --> 00:30:15,940
Where to? I just sat down.

543
00:30:17,260 --> 00:30:18,140
Haven't even eaten yet.

544
00:30:18,140 --> 00:30:18,780
Eat first.

545
00:30:22,140 --> 00:30:23,260
I'm afraid the two of us might

546
00:30:23,580 --> 00:30:25,020
interrupt your catch-up with Ms. Qin.

547
00:30:28,820 --> 00:30:30,420
Wei Ziming, stop being sarcastic.

548
00:30:30,740 --> 00:30:31,740
Enough, both of you.

549
00:30:33,340 --> 00:30:34,100
I'll go by myself.

550
00:30:36,460 --> 00:30:37,180
Zhizhi.

551
00:30:37,860 --> 00:30:39,660
Game over.

552
00:30:40,700 --> 00:30:42,140
Why did you bring up that photo?

553
00:30:43,020 --> 00:30:44,300
You should thank me.

554
00:30:44,460 --> 00:30:45,380
Look, she's jealous.

555
00:30:45,500 --> 00:30:46,700
That means she likes you.

556
00:30:51,260 --> 00:30:52,180
You should go check on her.

557
00:31:01,860 --> 00:31:02,740
Ms. Qin,

558
00:31:04,380 --> 00:31:06,060
am I just another piece
in your game too?

559
00:31:12,500 --> 00:31:13,300
What do you think?

560
00:31:25,500 --> 00:31:26,020
Zhizhi.

561
00:31:27,180 --> 00:31:28,100
You've got me wrong.

562
00:31:28,380 --> 00:31:29,420
What have I got wrong?

563
00:31:31,420 --> 00:31:34,020
You and your childhood sweetheart

564
00:31:34,380 --> 00:31:35,580
are back in a familiar place,

565
00:31:35,700 --> 00:31:36,740
